additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: Dosage form: Capsule, soft Quantity: 60 soft capsules Active ingredient per soft capsule: Fish oil natural 511.53 mg Docosahexaenoic Acid (DHA) 133 mg Eicosapentaenoic Acid (EPA) 28mg

additionalProperty.name: Contains
additionalProperty.value: Contains soya bean products, fish products sucralose and sulfites. Phenylketonurics - this product contains phenylalanine. 60 pack

additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Product to be used under adult supervision. For children unable to chew and swallow capsule, twist or cut off tail and squeeze into child's mouth or onto food. Contains fish products, soya bean products, sucralose and sulfites. Store below 25C. Protect from moisture. Do not use if tamper evident seal is broken or missing.
